283#define MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL 7
284
285enum SpellSchoolMask
286{
287 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NONE = 0x00, // not exist
288 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL = (1 << SPELL_SCHOOL_NORMAL), // PHYSICAL (Armor)
289 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_HOLY = (1 << SPELL_SCHOOL_HOLY),
290 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_FIRE = (1 << SPELL_SCHOOL_FIRE),
291 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NATURE = (1 << SPELL_SCHOOL_NATURE),
292 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_FROST = (1 << SPELL_SCHOOL_FROST),
293 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_SHADOW = (1 << SPELL_SCHOOL_SHADOW),
294 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_ARCANE = (1 << SPELL_SCHOOL_ARCANE),
295
296 // unions
297
298 // 124, not include normal and holy damage
299 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_SPELL = (SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_FIRE |
300 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NATURE | SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_FROST |
301 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_SHADOW | SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_ARCANE),
302 // 126
303 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_MAGIC = (SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_HOLY | SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_SPELL),
304
305 // 127
306 SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_ALL = (SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_NORMAL | SPELL_SCHOOL_MASK_MAGIC)
307};
308
309inline SpellSchools GetFirstSchoolInMask(SpellSchoolMask mask)
310{
311 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; ++i)
312 if (mask & (1 << i))
313 return SpellSchools(i);
314
315 return SPELL_SCHOOL_NORMAL;
316}

3862inline uint8 ClassByQuestSort(int32 QuestSort)
3863{
3864 switch (QuestSort)
3865 {
3866 case QUEST_SORT_WARLOCK: return CLASS_WARLOCK;
3867 case QUEST_SORT_WARRIOR: return CLASS_WARRIOR;
3868 case QUEST_SORT_SHAMAN: return CLASS_SHAMAN;
3869 case QUEST_SORT_PALADIN: return CLASS_PALADIN;
3870 case QUEST_SORT_MAGE: return CLASS_MAGE;
3871 case QUEST_SORT_ROGUE: return CLASS_ROGUE;
3872 case QUEST_SORT_HUNTER: return CLASS_HUNTER;
3873 case QUEST_SORT_PRIEST: return CLASS_PRIEST;
3874 case QUEST_SORT_DRUID: return CLASS_DRUID;
3875 case QUEST_SORT_DEATH_KNIGHT: return CLASS_DEATH_KNIGHT;
3876 }
3877 return 0;
3878}

4108inline SkillType SkillByLockType(LockType locktype)
4109{
4110 switch (locktype)
4111 {
4112 case LOCKTYPE_PICKLOCK: return SKILL_LOCKPICKING;
4113 case LOCKTYPE_HERBALISM: return SKILL_HERBALISM;
4114 case LOCKTYPE_MINING: return SKILL_MINING;
4115 case LOCKTYPE_FISHING: return SKILL_FISHING;
4116 case LOCKTYPE_INSCRIPTION: return SKILL_INSCRIPTION;
4117 default: break;
4118 }
4119 return SKILL_NONE;
4120}
